result.title: TCO18 Poland Regionals — University of Warsaw
result.content:
Topcoder Open is coming to Warsaw — Plan your date with TCO18 in Warsaw on 12th May 2018. Thank you to our sponsor University of Warsaw in Poland for supporting and hosting this event.

Register Now- https://tco18warsaw.eventbrite.com/

The event will include a Single Round Match (SRM) style Algorithm Competition that could lead you to the TCO18 Finals which will happen live at the event. The event will also allow you to mingle with other Topcoder members in your area, meet some cool sponsors, and get you a Topcoder t-shirt!

Parallel Fun Rated Round: There will be a Parallel Fun Rated Round for those not present onsite at the event.

Not to forget the amazing VR After Party -

Learn all about the event including the schedule and registration information here.

Register Now- https://tco18warsaw.eventbrite.com/

Schedule - 1:00 p.m. – 1:30 p.m. Registration, Check In, and T-shirt pickup

  • 1:30 p.m. – 1:45 p.m. Official welcome

  • 1:45 p.m. – 2:15 p.m. Presentation by a Topcoder member — Mojito1

  • 2:15 p.m. – 2:45 p.m. Algorithm Competition Set-Up and Registration

  • 2:45 p.m. – 4:45 p.m. Algorithm Competition

  • 4:45 p.m. – 5:00 p.m. Snack break

  • 5:00 p.m. — 5:30 p.m. Problem Set Analysis

  • 5:30 p.m. — 6:00 p.m Closing Reception & Results

  • 6:00 Onwards Virtual Reality Games Afterparty
